        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <form id="registerForm">
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="firstName" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">First Name</label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <input type="text" id="firstName">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="lastName" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Last Name</label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <input type="text" id="lastName">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="email" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Email</label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <input type="email" id="email">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="phone" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Phone Number</label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                <input type="tel" name="phone" id="phone">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="password" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Password</label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <input type="password" id="password">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="password2" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Confirm Password</label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <input type="password" id="password2">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="promocode" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Promo</label>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                  <input type="text" id="promocode">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="terms" class="radio">
                    <input type="radio" name="terms" id="terms" value="terms" class="radio__input">
                    <div class="radio__radio"></div>
                    i'm over 18 years old and i accpet the terms and conditions
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <label for="promotion" class="radio">
                    <input type="radio" name="promotion" id="promotion" value="1" class="radio__input">
                    <div class="radio__radio"></div>
                    Send me promotional materials
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
                <button class="btn btn-filled reg" type="submit" value="submit" name="submit">REGISTER</button>
            </div>
        </form>
        <div class="contianer">
            <p>
                Trading CFDs and Forex carries significant risks,including the loss of invested funds.<br>
